{"title":"长江源抒情诗","authors":["晏明"],"dates":[{"year":1988,"month":12,"day":25}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江源抒情诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晏明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当曲河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨曦的羽翼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扇起太阳的波涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光的血被融化了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰川峰尖闪露严寒的笑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰塔张开雪的帆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引出冰泉的浩渺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道细流撤开珠帘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涌起座座冰瀑滔滔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千条色彩斑斓的溪水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝陡峭的山坡跳跃奔跑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是母亲的最初的乳汁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哺育万里江流奔腾啸呼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏语意为“沼泽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河”，长江源头第二大河。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶鲁苏湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秀美的多尔改错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一支碧蓝醉人的歌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四周耸立淡红的山丘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖水闪着蓝宝石的浪波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧蓝的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧蓝的湖泊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上飞着天鹅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水上游着天鹅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵白云在湖中飘落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪是蓝天？哪是湖泊？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝宝石也在唱歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诱人的多尔改错……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶鲁苏湖的藏名为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“多尔改错”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直门达峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖，幽幽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峡谷，幽幽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岁月，在激浪中奔流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通天的河，通天的路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漩涡撕裂着漩涡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵谷奔腾而泻，涛声如鼓。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山的绮丽，岸的奇绝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千红，万紫，花如飞瀑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"径通八百里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亘古少行人惊涛洄洑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍天涯路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难越难越通天渡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直门达，悠悠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通天河，悠悠……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条幽深的高山峡谷，通天河流经此峡。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}